       Mutagenesis and ultraviolet inactivation of transforming DNA of
       Haemophilius influenzae complexed with a Bacillus sutilis protein
       that alters DNA conformation.
       Acta Biochim. Pol., 43(1), 107-114 (1996). Medline Abstract

